      "id": "134236571388087",
      "score": 4,
      "review_title": "Great educational value in context",
      "review_description": "One star detracted for grainy content. Updated cameras will provide crisper footage. This app lets you download videos onto the headset to improve speed of accessing the content. Great for classroom use. The content itself is best used within a broader instructional context. I highly recommend using the Okavango Delta videos in conjunction with the Google Earth tour: https://earth.app.goo.gl/ngiXjD. If you're in Georgia, contact education@gpb.org for information about a visit from our Mobile VR Lab. We can bring a class set of Oculus Go's to your school so students can experience VR first-hand!",
